{"tid":2090664,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"所有準備 send 文件做 BNO 既留意","createTime":"2020-07-02T09:32:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T12:38:24.000Z","uid":323480,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1104b63c2449ca45e2a637771ca4b75aa4daadaf","tid":2090664,"uid":323480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T09:32:52.000Z","msg":"我柒既，而家先黎整。我早兩日先 gather 好哂所有文件然後就去派件中心搞啦，佢地好熟手架啦，兩三下就搞掂哂。心諗寄到出去總算抖左啖氣。點知今朝我收到個電話，來電顯示係 +852 9xxx xxxx ，然後就電話錄音，claim 自己係 DHL 話我有個快件退回。我就呆一呆，之後仲有個語音查詢話廣東話按一字 國語/英文按咩字咁，我想知發生咩事我就按左 1 字啦，點知對面個把男人聲 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係講普通話</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我立馬 cut 線，攞返張單 number 上佢地 web site track 返, 個件一早到左 Liverpool。我又打去 DHL cs 同佢地講返件事。<br />\n個問題係，點會咁岩我前日寄完今日就有電話仲要話係 DHL ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋最大獲，知我電話 no. <br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲打，如果而家先黎搞 bno 既就小心 d, 我唔係話 DHL 信唔過，其實我覺得你地用其他公司都一樣會發生類似事件。總之一有電話打黎電話錄音話自己係邊間邊間公司就唔好聽啦。<br />\n<br />\n大家小心。"},{"pid":"8ac4d89d5a8d3958ba884fd5a1a128e3e23e62ca","tid":2090664,"uid":2772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T09:34:10.000Z","msg":"戇鳩<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"eefda33d6d894594e10f4a946a2488ceb954bb94","tid":2090664,"uid":33874,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T09:34:21.000Z","msg":"電話錄音已經cut得線啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8f4f8cc1bacaf6fae6a8bf6d6f1112f3283835","tid":2090664,"uid":195,"like":1,"